woo, new girly layout and new icon in one day! I'm on a roll.

I'm no longer the green goblin. I'm not evil enough. I'll leave it to howie. I've decided that I am most definately a changeling.

I went exploring today, like the little adventurer that I am. I was at my nan's, and I decided to explore her basement for the billionth time. My mind is ever-changing, and I'm always finding something new to love that I didn't love before. Today I found a mexican blanket, a patchwork plaid blanket my great grandmother made, a bunch of feathery things, a cool lunch bag, and a little sand-filled beany frog. I had to smuggle it out all stealthy like. My nan doesn't care if I take stuff, but I just like being stealthy. It's good to train for the days when I will accept my fairy heritage and will have to sneak around at night, blessing peoples' homes with my fairy magic.

http://hipforums.com/forums/showthread.php?t=74560

beauty :)

~Leah Dawn
